						<h3 ><a href="#p52043">Re: SNAKE.BAT 4.0 - An arcade style game using pure batch</a></h3>

													<ul class="post-buttons">
																																									<li>
							<a href="postingdfa9.php?mode=quote&amp;f=3&amp;p=52043" title="Reply with quote" class="button button-icon-only">
